OL,3,CChris Evans shares family's plea after
OL,4,Cdeath of boy at CarFest
OL,6,FCarFest founder Chris Evans has
OL,7,Faddressed the death of a child at his
OL,8,Ffestival and has shared a plea from
OL,9,Fthe family for people to download the
OL,10,FWhat Three Words app.
OL,12,FA boy was treated by emergency
OL,13,Fservices at the festival at Laverstoke
OL,14,FPark Farm in Hampshire on Saturday, 24
OL,15,FAugust, but later died in hospital.
OL,17,FThe radio DJ said the boy's family was
OL,18,F"amazing" and added that they had
OL,19,Fknown his death was coming and
OL,20,F"treasured the dawning of every new
OL,21,Fday" with him.
