OL,3,CChris Evans shares family's plea after
OL,4,Cdeath of boy at CarFest
OL,6,FSpeaking on his Virgin Radio show,
OL,7,FEvans said: "On Wednesday afternoon,
OL,8,Fthe little boy's dad reached out to me
OL,9,Fvia a telephone call and requested I
OL,10,Fmake a sincere plea to anyone and
OL,11,Feveryone going forward.
OL,13,F"As the little boy's dad is in no
OL,14,Fdoubt whatsoever that What Three Words
OL,15,Fwas instrumental in enabling the
OL,16,Femergency services to identify his
OL,17,Fprecise location at the accessibility
OL,18,Fcampsite up at CarFest, and therefore
OL,19,Fattend the scene of his son's serious
OL,20,Fmedical emergency as soon as it was
OL,21,Fhumanly possible.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
