OL,3,CChris Evans shares family's plea after
OL,4,Cdeath of boy at CarFest
OL,6,F"Tragically, as we now know, despite
OL,7,Fall their best efforts, they were
OL,8,Fstill unable to save the little boy.
OL,9,FBut his dad remains insistent that
OL,10,FWhat Three Words gave those
OL,11,Fprofessionals best equipped to help,
OL,12,Fthe best chance of helping."
OL,14,FHe went on to describe the family as
OL,15,F"selfless" for thinking about others
OL,16,Fwho could be saved by the app after
OL,17,Ftheir son's death.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
