OL,3,CChris Evans shares family's plea after
OL,4,Cdeath of boy at CarFest
OL,6,F"His mum and dad always knew this day
OL,7,Fwas going to come, and they were aware
OL,8,Fthat it was more likely going to be
OL,9,Fsooner rather than later, and
OL,10,Ftherefore treasured the dawning of
OL,11,Fevery new day. He was still with them.
OL,13,F"From what I've learned, from what
OL,14,FI've heard over the last week, it
OL,15,Fseems not a moment went by when they
OL,16,Fweren't giving it their all to ensure
OL,17,Fhe was being loved as much as anyone
OL,18,Fhas ever been loved before.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
