OL,3,CChris Evans shares family's plea after
OL,4,Cdeath of boy at CarFest
OL,6,F"It is therefore, with their
OL,7,Fpermission and only with their
OL,8,Fexplicit permission, which I am yet to
OL,9,Fgain, that next year's CarFest will be
OL,10,Fheld in this little boy's name."
OL,12,FHampshire and Isle of Wight Air
OL,13,FAmbulance confirmed that an air
OL,14,Fambulance, carrying a doctor and
OL,15,Fspecialist paramedic, was dispatched
OL,16,Fto the incident in Basingstoke on
OL,17,FSaturday, 24 August.
