OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "Following
OL,7,Ftreatment on scene, a patient was
OL,8,Ftaken to hospital by road ambulance
OL,9,Ffor further treatment.
OL,11,F"The air ambulance team travelled with
OL,12,Fthe patient to continue providing
OL,13,Fspecialist care."
OL,15,FThe event raises funds for charities
OL,16,Fincluding Children In Need, Young
OL,17,FEpilepsy, Ellen MacArthur Cancer
OL,18,FTrust, My Black Dog, Rainbow Trust,
OL,19,FStarlight Children's Foundation and
OL,20,FTeenage Cancer Trust.
